00:37:26,750 --> 00:37:27,670
Now it's the eve of it.

857
00:37:27,670 --> 00:37:29,870
Captain, it's too early to wish me a Happy Chinese New Year.

858
00:37:29,870 --> 00:37:31,220
For the safety of your residence,

859
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:32,770
and to ensure you and your family

860
00:37:32,770 --> 00:37:33,900
will have a Happy Chinese New Year,

861
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:34,980
I have to be here.

862
00:37:35,130 --> 00:37:36,330
Just cut to the chase.

863
00:37:37,530 --> 00:37:39,130
Can we have a word in private?

864
00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:39,680
No need.

865
00:37:39,830 --> 00:37:40,990
I'm a man of integrity.

866
00:37:40,990 --> 00:37:43,390
There's nothing I need to hide from others.

867
00:37:44,290 --> 00:37:45,690
Then I'll level with you.

868
00:37:46,180 --> 00:37:48,980
Previously, an informant of mine named Li Shengda

869
00:37:49,220 --> 00:37:50,330
was assassinated.

870
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:51,660
Coincidentally,

871
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:52,720
Zhang Mingquan came and reported a crime,

872
00:37:52,720 --> 00:37:55,520
saying that his gun was taken away at the New Show Club.

873
00:37:55,520 --> 00:37:56,920
We found an eyewitness.

874
00:37:57,340 --> 00:37:58,940
This eyewitness identified

875
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:00,480
the robber

876
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:02,100
as your personal assistant,

877
00:38:02,250 --> 00:38:03,160
Wei Ruolai.

878
00:38:09,820 --> 00:38:10,620
Captain Lin,

879
00:38:11,350 --> 00:38:12,750
would you mind telling me

880
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:14,370
who this eyewitness is?

881
00:38:14,370 --> 00:38:15,430
It's an old beggar.

882
00:38:16,140 --> 00:38:18,270
He said after you robbed Zhang Mingquan,

883
00:38:18,270 --> 00:38:20,200
you threw his wallet and pocket watch

884
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:21,480
into a trash can.

885
00:38:21,560 --> 00:38:22,850
He happened to see all that.

886
00:38:22,850 --> 00:38:24,890
So you think you can arrest me

887
00:38:24,910 --> 00:38:25,630
based on a beggar's statement?

888
00:38:25,630 --> 00:38:26,710
We're from the Investigation and Arrest Unit.

889
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:28,550
We wouldn't come find you without proof.

890
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:30,880
More importantly, Mr. Shen is right here.

891
00:38:31,110 --> 00:38:32,490
I wouldn't dare to make a wrong arrest.

892
00:38:32,490 --> 00:38:33,670
After we got the beggar's statement,

893
00:38:33,670 --> 00:38:34,270
we examined

894
00:38:34,270 --> 00:38:37,200
the fingerprints on the wallet and the pocket watch.

895
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:39,130
We found a perfect match to those

896
00:38:39,430 --> 00:38:41,490
you left on the letter of confession.

897
00:38:41,490 --> 00:38:42,840
You don't have to take the witness's word.

898
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:44,040
But the fingerprints

899
00:38:44,100 --> 00:38:46,560
are no doubt qualified to be legal evidence.

900
00:38:50,290 --> 00:38:52,550
Fingerprints can be forged, can't they?

901
00:38:52,730 --> 00:38:53,370
Mr. Shen,

902
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:55,200
we've sent people

903
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:57,080
to search Wei Ruolai's home.

904
00:38:57,210 --> 00:38:57,910
Care to guess

905
00:38:57,910 --> 00:38:58,880
what we found?

906
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:00,490
What did you find?

907
00:39:00,490 --> 00:39:00,980
A gun.

908
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:01,950
It's Zhang Mingquan's gun.

909
00:39:01,950 --> 00:39:02,770
Are his fingerprints on the gun?

910
00:39:02,770 --> 00:39:03,310
Yes.

911
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:07,900
Say it. Give him an explanation.

912
00:39:12,290 --> 00:39:12,970
It's true.

913
00:39:13,410 --> 00:39:14,790
I did rob Zhang Mingquan of his gun,

914
00:39:14,790 --> 00:39:16,390
but I didn't kill Li Shengda.

915
00:39:16,700 --> 00:39:18,160
After I gave Li the seal and key,

916
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:19,620
I've never seen him again.

917
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:20,670
An interrogation

918
00:39:20,780 --> 00:39:22,000
will help us find out the truth.

919
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:22,710
Well, Mr. Shen...

920
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:23,490
What gives you the right to arrest him?

921
00:39:23,490 --> 00:39:24,190
Shut up.

922
00:39:25,970 --> 00:39:27,440
Mr. Shen, can I

923
00:39:28,220 --> 00:39:29,220
arrest him or not?

924
00:39:32,900 --> 00:39:33,530
You can.

925
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,030
Please.

926
00:39:44,610 --> 00:39:45,350
Sorry for the intrusion, Mr. Shen.

927
00:39:45,350 --> 00:39:45,900
Your coat.

928
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:47,230
Happy Chinese New Year.

929
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:53,450
Tunan,

930
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:56,760
Wei Ruolai doesn't seem to be a killer.

931
00:39:57,030 --> 00:39:58,960
Then why did he rob Zhang of his gun?

932
00:40:04,170 --> 00:40:05,770
If he's cornered,

933
00:40:06,160 --> 00:40:07,430
will he do some crazy stuff?

934
00:40:07,430 --> 00:40:08,160
He sure will.

935
00:40:08,430 --> 00:40:10,600
Political influence aside,

936
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:13,630
assassination is the most cost-effective solution.

937
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:14,840
Then I'll apply for a gun.

938
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:15,450
No.

939
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,950
You are my assistant,

940
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:19,240
not my bodyguard.

941
00:40:19,580 --> 00:40:21,530
You just do your job.

942
00:40:21,710 --> 00:40:22,190
Yes.

943
00:40:29,060 --> 00:40:30,720
Wei Ruolai is your assistant.

944
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:32,290
If he's incriminated,

945
00:40:32,680 --> 00:40:33,410
I'm afraid

946
00:40:34,100 --> 00:40:36,030
you'll become collateral damage.

947
00:40:36,530 --> 00:40:37,150
I know.

948
00:40:37,710 --> 00:40:38,900
I can make this gun robbery thing go away.

949
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:40,300
But if he did kill someone

950
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:44,180
who worked as an informant for the Investigation and Arrest Unit,

951
00:40:45,470 --> 00:40:46,530
no one can help him.

952
00:40:57,420 --> 00:40:58,090
Tell me.

953
00:40:58,740 --> 00:41:00,270
Why did you kill Li Shengda?

954
00:41:06,240 --> 00:41:08,640
Where is the gold that was placed in the box?

955
00:41:16,720 --> 00:41:17,790
Spill it!

956
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:20,820
Confess before it's too late!

957
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,240
Wenbiao.

958
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:35,640
Captain Lin.

959
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,120
Sir.

960
00:41:44,890 --> 00:41:45,620
Torture him.

961
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:50,860
Does my order mean nothing to you?

962
00:41:52,210 --> 00:41:52,850
Da Li!

963
00:41:53,230 --> 00:41:53,830
Yes!

964
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:55,510
Go!

965
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:02,520
Which protocol?

966
00:42:02,710 --> 00:42:03,510
The third one.

967
00:42:05,370 --> 00:42:07,200
Are you gonna say it or not?

968
00:42:07,710 --> 00:42:09,710
Tell the truth! Did you kill the man?

969
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:13,950
Are you gonna say it or not?

970
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:19,790
Sir,

971
00:42:20,070 --> 00:42:21,740
you ordered to torture him right in the beginning.

972
00:42:21,740 --> 00:42:23,540
It doesn't seem like your style.

973
00:42:24,620 --> 00:42:26,000
He works for Shen Tunan.

974
00:42:27,070 --> 00:42:28,530
Mr. Kang's breathing down my neck.

975
00:42:28,530 --> 00:42:30,790
I need to show my stance by torturing him.

976
00:42:32,460 --> 00:42:33,920
But if we go too rough on him

977
00:42:34,440 --> 00:42:36,440
only to find out he's not the killer,

978
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:38,520
we can't give Shen Tunan

979
00:42:38,720 --> 00:42:40,250
a reasonable explanation.

980
00:42:41,970 --> 00:42:43,070
How is he not the killer?

981
00:42:43,070 --> 00:42:44,440
He must've killed the man!

982
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:46,590
Whether he's the killer or not doesn't matter now.

983
00:42:46,590 --> 00:42:49,190
Mr. Kang is using Wei Ruolai as a pawn

984
00:42:49,550 --> 00:42:51,150
to fight against Shen Tunan.

985
00:42:51,350 --> 00:42:52,950
I might as well use Wei Ruolai

986
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:55,640
to find new clues about the communists.

987
00:42:55,890 --> 00:42:56,650
No collision of interests.
